{"tid":1292103,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"養狗高手拯救我","createTime":"2019-07-07T07:08:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T05:51:29.000Z","uid":257779,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"aecbad804b79526dffd04cab4b10b9ed9b52efb7","tid":1292103,"uid":257779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T07:08:02.000Z","msg":"琴日接咗領養嘅唐狗bb返屋企，兩個月大，由兩個禮拜起已經係暫養嘅地方學識跟其他大狗定點大小便。一返到嚟比咗個細空間（六塊嘅圍欄）佢活動，咁當然佢係非常不安緊張，一離開佢就嗚嗚叫，所以琴晩訓梳化陪佢。試過比佢擴大少少個範圍，但就即刻周圍痾屎痾尿，所以都係縮小返到床仔、少少地板位同個廁所板。<br />\n而家佢一見唔到人就痾尿係圍欄邊，所以我就索咗佢嘅尿係塊毛巾擺係佢廁所板上。<br />\n所以想問下巴絲打們啱啱接幼犬返屋企點解決佢嘅不安感唔好周圍痾大痾小，而家已經24/7咁陪佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f84ddd70e930f845fe3d6a1a6525fe41e08ce511","tid":1292103,"uid":213636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T07:09:05.000Z","msg":"比條毛巾/公仔佢？"},{"pid":"4ddc3a0d7bd214de1699a67f599f98155ab0dfcd","tid":1292103,"uid":257779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f84ddd70e930f845fe3d6a1a6525fe41e08ce511","tid":1292103,"uid":213636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T07:09:05.000Z","msg":"比條毛巾/公仔佢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T07:10:07.000Z","msg":"已經比咗好多佢，但係佢都冇乜安全感，對公仔玩具都冇興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c900c3cb5400298801e8c609d949d72ae9531066","tid":1292103,"uid":275370,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T07:12:07.000Z","msg":"見到佢想痾果陣dump佢落廁所"},{"pid":"dbad183825c33b0c6187a95a65032a6e791e2e46","tid":1292103,"uid":213636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ddc3a0d7bd214de1699a67f599f98155ab0dfcd","tid":1292103,"uid":257779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f84ddd70e930f845fe3d6a1a6525fe41e08ce511","tid":1292103,"uid":213636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T07:09:05.000Z","msg":"比條毛巾/公仔佢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T07:10:07.000